text: Jordyn Marie Wieber (born July 12, 1995) is an American artistic gymnast. She was a member of the gold medal-winning US women's gymnastics teams at the 2011 World Championships. Wieber was a team gold medalist at the 2012 Summer Olympics. She was also the 2011 world women's all-around champion. == References == Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic gold medalists for the United States Category:American gymnasts
